fo_overview: .406 Ventures is an early stage venture capital firm that invests in innovative Information Technology (IT) and services companies founded by the finest entrepreneurs. They are a veteran team of industry entrepreneurs operators and investors who apply real world experience deep industry knowledge and networks and strong company building skills to create value for our entrepreneurs and investing partners..406 Ventures typically are the lead first institutional investor in early stage and de novo investments in market changing IT Security and Infrastructure Technology Enabled Business Services and Next Generation Software companies.
